ass=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0b98bd73-a4c4-4543-b326-dbc5e40859f1\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-64766470-603c-4af8-bdeb-705241cfef69\">그런데 한의학에서는 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-21bd308e-888a-4d3d-8414-a546c7482b76\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-6c9059de-fa08-4b96-8004-da323ec097f6\">이 문제를 단순히 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-8e343605-6dd6-4f75-8712-cff5bd51503f\"><b>스트레스나 카페인 때문</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-91b90f1e-7515-48d1-812a-71d13ae11430\">으로만 보지 않습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-cbc5c2e2-d2d0-407f-84f2-f5ef1c4e8592\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-360971c5-f2d8-4115-a01c-a709c351845f\"><b>사상체질(四象體質)</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-3707698d-b6d8-4820-8a7e-de476961048a\"> 이론에 따르면, </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1e32aac5-b6ed-4a8f-989a-f706b7274aee\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-178087fb-f4d7-43a7-9933-f180db521eb4\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6d003410-53c1-4abd-a488-baddc262e67a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-fafb0d02-ce0d-4d5b-b13a-0a3dbc922c6e\">사람마다 타고난 기질과 장부의 기능이 다르기 때문에</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0d3a9e42-b915-4215-a7ce-c06491905427\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-8743194e-3d42-4032-992f-5439e139ffa2\"><b>체질에 따라 수면의 질, 수면 시간, 쉽게 잠드는 시간대</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-4c9cdb9a-1ca2-40b4-af94-2ed788b2ecde\">까지도 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3b83d09f-a63c-4e03-908d-d59fc3f70726\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-82de1bf1-9e55-44e6-8091-a418834ba76c\">달라질 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-e967f252-2979-44f8-99ba-6b560a31d24a\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-6275b4ff-fd86-42aa-9906-d3e8a5e12ae4\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a52c1d4b-ef12-4a25-a248-4dd75489e66f\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-a52c1d4b-ef12-4a25-a248-4dd75489e66f\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/185342836c0ee6cf.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1600\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1600\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/185342836c0ee6cf.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/185342836c0ee6cf.png\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"500\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_image\", \"id\": \"SE-a52c1d4b-ef12-4a25-a248-4dd75489e66f\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"ai\": \"false\" }}'></script>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-90b67ae7-f562-4a88-96b2-b8fdc5e2aad4\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n                            <blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-85734ede-c0a2-445e-9cde-f908d1472751\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d86ef644-9bae-4b95-a928-41a0313efdfa\"><b>체질별 수면 특징과 개선법</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                            </blockquote>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d9e8ec2c-712e-46a9-b903-58d32ad1b40c\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-135b27bd-a153-44e7-b29f-ef505fe05dad\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-baaf26cc-2ad9-4418-8818-7ea01ff19058\"><b>🌿 태양인</b></span></p><ul class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-bullet-disc\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8b3b5d5b-bfcd-4ae6-a817-0769e01b7273\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-2e214aff-ba2c-4c91-a8fb-66fd5c28d156\"><b>특징</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-894a22a1-4263-4011-9423-612366b171da\">: 폐가 약하고 간 기능이 강한 체질</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4de5f71d-2721-4893-97be-741dcb088bcd\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-04e05f88-3eae-4ce4-8a98-1911ceceeccc\"><b>수면 문제</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-1e83abc3-e4ec-4f0c-b43f-ed99853749ed\">: 머리가 맑지 않고, 쉽게 흥분하거나 화를 잘 냄</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ec970f65-5b9a-4064-a92f-cd08c36fc9fd\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-e3b13664-a778-4a4a-82bb-22dfb718035c\"><b>수면 팁</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-92d54794-0b1e-467a-885d-4edd42f8c6fa\">:</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c2b225cf-5949-4d2b-a44c-c771c6cc6dfe\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-960fb407-a0d5-4edf-bd27-a96635670bd1\">낮에는 활동량을 충분히 늘려야 밤에 깊이 잠들 수 있음</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1c3cbd48-7403-42ef-841d-719e543b5133\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-625eb3e1-0738-402b-9e83-a3a0053d001c\"><b>심호흡과 스트레칭</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-9cb5e9a1-f26c-4c4b-a5a9-b58d20dfd18c\">으로 흥분된 기운을 가라앉히는 것이 중요</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-183ed865-b456-4468-9146-9742b18557bc\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-9f288b88-c6e5-4002-88eb-eb1e3e9a99a6\">밤 늦게까지 스마트폰 보는 습관은 반드시 줄일 것</span></p></li></ul><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3db8ea47-32a1-4b1d-86ae-83e4d73d237b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-5297e056-18a1-4e70-bb91-ff604871522b\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-17d1c498-71ec-4bd3-9226-c62c1fb5f569\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-8604ce5a-d4eb-4755-b444-c8f40af97b29\"><b>🌳 태음인</b></span></p><ul class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-bullet-disc\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-418ea2ab-060c-4425-954c-d193a4b43958\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-b2e8d047-b844-40ab-b3d6-30c063781126\"><b>특징</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-df79d7d7-c4da-4296-8c3b-a9f106551a76\">: 간 기능이 약하고 폐가 강함</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6738992d-2610-4e35-b7b4-3a4162e74563\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-e9860757-66a3-48a4-a5c5-5d84bd24d324\"><b>수면 문제</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-1fb6a7cf-4f18-401e-8849-a0745678cf8e\">: 과식 후 더위를 느끼며 숙면이 어려움, 무기력과 피로감이 많음</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3e32e7b5-39dd-4210-ba27-d68450a98e97\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-134e0a50-70e5-42ac-aac6-d144810ae18f\"><b>수면 팁</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-25739762-3fde-42e1-8d6a-ecdbfa3bbdcd\">:</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4a3b14c2-a27c-4d6f-9a40-ca40d076d79c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-fbbedd58-321b-4f3a-8da7-3f5b74e696c2\"><b>과식 피하기</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-27a3196e-8daa-4f32-9814-d4ccecda522f\">, 특히 자기 전 3시간 금식</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-09697d93-545e-4af9-b96e-82b908d12a30\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-1dbbb7a9-2379-40f5-a695-7916b68c556b\">적절한 운동으로 땀을 내어 순환을 도우면 수면 질이 좋아짐</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-612ce497-2423-45c3-881e-43c64377f3f2\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-f287fdba-86c8-43e3-9503-a4f2923b957a\">침실 온도는 약간 서늘하게 유지</span></p></li></ul><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-25f3aa51-5676-4be5-8dcd-efb32c2ee1e1\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-9392be36-b662-4a38-94da-827aef88016e\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ae028615-1da3-4b90-b0c5-d0cab228be28\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-ceafeb91-a4ce-4a86-91fb-cbdf2dc37f3b\"><b>🔥 소양인</b></span></p><ul class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-bullet-disc\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0b04b067-bae0-4d5c-9d88-767992eae251\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-5312bbb4-d26f-4b91-9975-8dcaa2da429e\"><b>특징</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-7159e454-e501-4bde-a11f-28bafda005d3\">: 열이 많고 흥분·긴장이 빠른 체질</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-61d86c37-5075-42d9-a4c0-eac0bf5f6b8f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-b800d823-18ed-4d86-8277-fc49f864dff5\"><b>수면 문제</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-da9b87f7-993d-446b-a8b0-833e0973058d\">: 잠드는 시간이 늦어지고 자주 깨는 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-24ce6620-098e-4c6e-801d-b076e2db657d\"><b>중간각성</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-0b92114e-83cf-4742-be07-5a701a5cfabf\">이 많음</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-65489611-8f8b-4622-8b39-1f2d22303dfd\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-78db46f0-20ae-4109-a926-7cdae7edc183\"><b>수면 팁</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-d7928ea8-1f45-4d1f-be3e-9ef3d2c0b7b8\">:</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c6e08a71-f595-4a82-9ac2-00c173796d0b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-1a1d7b5b-2510-4261-8acc-23b05000d8f3\">**몸을 식혀주는 식단(연근, 오이, 녹두차 등)**과 함께 카페인 줄이기</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-f3270f68-b12c-4066-b0d9-2f05fee2f0ee\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-415a294a-64e6-4fa6-9c64-4d9860fd4e5f\">수면 전 강한 운동은 피하고, 명상·스트레칭 등으로 진정 필요</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d1b1b7b8-c8f2-4d73-bc26-bebd7f28481f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-ca714d1b-7cc0-429e-915c-9c7ca0c51b1b\"><b>두피나 목 뒷부분을 시원하게 해주는 찜질팩</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-4c792c79-6ff3-49a3-b3fe-f03f27c4a4fb\">도 도움</span></p></li></ul><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d1a3f2c1-ddd5-4b73-981b-8e90f0d5393e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-288eb55f-74a5-487b-8bf7-da04899e28a5\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a37e387f-38b7-417a-aabd-1c2f40ce662e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-c67cdcd0-2b9a-4aed-92d4-6593b6599d48\"><b>🌰 소음인</b></span></p><ul class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-bullet-disc\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1de01075-af5f-4377-80b4-53f3069d2bc5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-c72aed1e-764b-4986-afeb-7e4b4fd6aef1\"><b>특징</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-6a0ba666-35b9-4833-927c-392f97a41e75\">: 위장 기능 약하고 수족이 차가움</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-69663dcb-309e-4cac-82bf-3130485a4911\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-97830873-2ae6-4162-bf7e-ab30702c9196\"><b>수면 문제</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-ce89a981-5b60-4d3a-bf45-3947536acd63\">: 쉽게 피곤해지고, 잠은 많지만 깊게 자지 못함</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7ea40466-165b-451e-811c-8a398fea18b9\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-7e03b17e-5d95-4b70-b146-39b9029c739e\"><b>수면 팁</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-e93a60e2-b802-4548-90ed-009ba03ebc0f\">:</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-af03b3fd-6dd8-4577-b391-c14a343f592c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-94906079-86c2-488e-be5e-4504c88b3c3a\">잠들기 전 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-2db233e9-c606-475f-8318-bac6157e7102\"><b>따뜻한 차(대추차, 생강차)</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-4ae53da1-b5e0-4cfe-92c8-834b3b12bd11\"> 마시기</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7c9534f0-9643-469c-894e-8d085ae3986b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-e08a8a47-0b61-4f3b-a884-4680655bb991\">배와 발을 따뜻하게 한 후 수면 유도</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7393906f-9164-4349-b7bb-8cbf4b939e53\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-654d9fe3-7626-43cc-9d75-944710f3fdbe\">지나치게 많은 수면은 피하고 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-683778ae-1614-4fda-a7c4-09b1197beca7\"><b>일정한 기상 시간 유지</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-c2534e52-1696-4371-a60c-4c6f659e4e4a\">가 중요</span></p></li></ul><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-d9e8ec2c-712e-46a9-b903-58d32ad1b40c\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d3f43950-d479-4571-aa74-d148d79bf7f1\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\