module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-22ada708-e20a-4f69-a5c4-f8ae7e1ebef7\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b59e8243-042e-49c8-bc22-eb114204b770\"><b>공통 수면 건강 팁</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                            </blockquote>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9acfac2a-7049-46e8-ae3b-f9bc41611dd5\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><ul class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-bullet-disc\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-82a76912-ae61-4603-a0e7-84759013a982\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-eac6f694-ce4c-424b-8f4e-e0b6567ce29a\"><b>매일 같은 시간에 자고 일어나기 (기상 시간 고정)</b></span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c1818f24-ebc6-44ac-b8d1-9ad6f7bfa84d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-490242da-6e66-4c15-b154-2d272ec9d00d\"><b>취침 1시간 전 스마트폰·TV 자제</b></span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1b881b2e-6a5a-453d-b3ec-d64ca453eb0e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-706f8384-6ce7-4e06-bc2e-d4fce82fc938\"><b>카페인, 술, 단 음식은 늦은 시간 피하기</b></span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ccfe026f-42e2-4628-9d4c-2f02b212edc4\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-6bc09217-3f72-4004-a070-c692db24329d\"><b>수면일지를 써보며 내 